name: Electra The Electrician
description: Electra was an electrician in Dr. Enky's lab. He immediately rushed his way when he hear strange noises inside Dr's experiment room. By the time he arrived there, he found Dr. Enky and Carbac has changed their form into soulless creatures. He watched the powerful stone on Dr's chest, while he was thinking of what it is, he lost his consciousness and become a soulless creature just like Dr. Enky and Carbac.
